<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT80">
<l>viraintaṭaimiṉ mēloruṉāḷ veḷḷam parakka</l>
<l>karantulakaṅ kāttaḷitta kaṇṇaṉ parantulakam</l>
<l>pāṭiṉa vāṭiṉa kēṭṭu paṭuṉarakam</l>
<l>vīṭiṉa vācaṟ katavu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Swiftly reach Kṛṣṇa, who guarded against [sorrows], protected,</l>
<l rend="indent">and sheltered the world, concealing [it in His belly]</l>
<l>as floods spread [everywhere] on a day in the past.</l>
<l>The entrance doors of cruel hell were destroyed</l>
<l>hearing the singing [and] the dancing of the [people of the] world</l>
<l rend="indent">spreading [everywhere].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
